getSubStrings

public static final java.util.List<StringWrapper.SubString> getSubStrings(Parser.Parse parse,
                                                                          java.util.Set<java.lang.String> nodeNames)
Utility method to extract substrings from the parse for parse nodes that have any of the given node (category) names.

Note that all text under a node will be concatenated together and returned as a single substring.

Each substring will have a 'category' attribute that identifies which nodeName was matched while extracting the substring from the parse tree.
